        "can_see_hidden_post": false,
        "can_unaccept_answer": false,
        "can_view_edit_history": true,
        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>I fully understand and i agree. The question is if we could have some kind of template where placeholders could be used so the creator could customize the download name. Or allow to provide the name as OpenScad Variable that we need to \u201cecho\u201d in a certain way so the infrastructure can pick it up.</p>\n<p>Example:<br>\n\u201cOrganizer Box xx - Corner \u201d</p>",
        "created_at": "2025-06-27T09:53:25.180Z",
        "current_user_reaction": null,
        "current_user_used_main_reaction": false,
        "deleted_at": null,
